    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "明日はのんびり出来ると思ってたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought we’d be able to take it easy tomorrow‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.488027219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "直前になってイベントの仕事が入るなんてなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but then an event job comes in at the last minute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "文句を言っても仕方ないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Complaining won’t do any good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3309977492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "私達は受けた仕事を全力でやり遂げるだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once we take a job‚ we give it our best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。お仕事だから仕方ないよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. It’s work‚ so it can’t be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4176643014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（せっかく準備したのに、クリスマスパーティーも）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The Christmas party I did all the preparations for)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7985259335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "（出来なくなっちゃったな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(is not going to happen.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そろそろレッスンを始めましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s nearly time to start the lesson.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "明日の本番に向けて精度を上げるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have to get more precise before we’re doing this on stage tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今日は時間がかかりそうやな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks like this will take quite a while today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんは夜遅くなっても大丈夫なん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will you be okay even if it gets late‚ Sumire-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "今夜は寮の部屋に泊まるから平気だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be staying in my dorm room tonight‚ so it’s fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "寮かあ……。前は遅くなると、うちか瑠依ちゃんの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your room… That sounds lonely. Normally if we get late‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "部屋に泊まってたのになんか寂しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you stay with me or Rui-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一人が寂しかったらうちの部屋に泊まりに来てもええよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re lonely on your own‚ you can sleep over in my room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんならいつでもウェルカムや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re always welcome‚ Sumire-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.11,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ありがとう。でもこういう時のために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. But for this time‚ I had my",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "寮に私の部屋を作ってもらったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "dorm room made up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつも実家から通ってるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I always commute back to my parents’ house‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "こんな時くらいは部屋を使ってあげないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but at least at times like this‚ I should use my room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本当に一人で平気？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re really alright alone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "寂しくなったらいつでも私達の部屋に来ていいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you get lonely‚ you can come over to our rooms any time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.51,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "二人ともありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you both.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "でもいつものことだから大丈夫だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this happens a lot‚ so it’s fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……そうだよ。急な仕事だっていつものことなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re always getting sudden jobs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "早く気持ちを切り替えなくちゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to move on with it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、レッスン頑張るぞー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ let’s do our best in the lesson!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうしたの、すみれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s the matter‚ Sumire-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "さっきから同じ所でミスして、あなたらしくないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You keep making a mistake in the same place. That’s not like you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、なんだか集中出来なくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ I just can’t concentrate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本番は明日なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And the real show is tomorrow…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "早く気持ちを切り替えなきゃいけないのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to move on already…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すみれちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "明日の休み、ほんまに楽しみにしてたんやなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you were really looking forward to our day off tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん……私、自分で思ってたよりずっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I guess I’ve been looking forward to it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
